The paper proposes a new intelligent fault diagnosis framework using deep learning and transfer learning techniques. It involves adapting the conditional distribution of unlabeled target data using discrimination structures associated with labeled data in the source domain. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the following arXiv CS sub-categories: 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning)
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence)
- cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition)
- cs.SY (Systems and Control)
- cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing)
